      <h1 class="title">
      #você.serpro: a rede social corporativa, em Noosfero, do Serpro
  </h1>
  <span class="publishing-info">
  <span class="date">
    Luglio 12, 2013 0:00
  </span>
  <span class="author">
    , by Aurélio A. Heckert
  </span>
  <span class="comments">
     - <a href="/colivre/blog/voce.serpro-a-rede-social-corporativa-em-noosfero-do-serpro#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>no comments yet</span></a>
  </span>

